comments: Caruso (LAL) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.

Horton-Tucker (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (DEN) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.

Gasol (LAL) grabs Jokic's (DEN) arm prior to his gather and a non-shooting foul should have been called.
